               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Introduction (fols. 6r – 8v)&#xD;
-  Canon Tables (fols. 6r - 8v)&#xD;
II) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 10ra – 40vb)&#xD;
- Bәsratä Matewos “Gospel of Matthew” (fols. 10ra – 40rb [l.6])&#xD;
- Short postscript (fol. 40ra [ls. 15-18] – rb [ls. 15-18])&#xD;
- Stichometry (fol. 40ra [l.20])&#xD;
- List of the “Tituli” for the Gospel of Matthew - 65 titles (fol. 40vab)&#xD;
III) Gospel of Mark (fols. 42ra – 60ra)&#xD;
- Bәsratä Marqos “Gospel of Mark” (fols. 42ra – 60ra)&#xD;
IV) Gospel of Luke (fols. 62ra – 94vb)&#xD;
- Bәsratä Luqas (fols. 62ra – 94vb)&#xD;
V) Gospel of John (fols. 96ra – 120vb)&#xD;
- Bәsratä Yoḥannәs “Gospel of John” (fols. 96ra – 120vb [l.13])&#xD;
- Stichometry (fol. 120vb [ls. 17-18])&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-5.</summary>
